<view class="login-page">
  <view class="bg bg-1"></view>
  <view class="bg bg-2"></view>

  <view class="login-wrapper">
    <view class="brand-box">
      <view class="brand-badge">S</view>
      <view class="brand-text">
        <view class="brand-title">SPHAS 健康助手</view>
        <view class="brand-subtitle">账号登录和微信快捷登录都支持</view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="login-card">
      <view class="card-title">欢迎登录</view>
      <view class="card-desc">登录后可查看健康记录、推荐内容和个人数据</view>

      <view class="form-item">
        <view class="label">账号 / 手机号</view>
        <view class="input-wrap">
          <input
            class="input"
            placeholder="请输入账号或手机号"
            placeholder-class="ph"
            value="{{account}}"
            bindinput="onAccount"
          />
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="form-item">
        <view class="label">密码</view>
        <view class="input-wrap">
          <input
            class="input"
            password
            placeholder="请输入密码"
            placeholder-class="ph"
            value="{{password}}"
            bindinput="onPassword"
          />
        </view>
      </view>

      <button
        class="login-btn"
        loading="{{loading}}"
        disabled="{{loading || wxLoading}}"
        bindtap="onLogin"
      >
        {{loading ? '登录中...' : '账号登录'}}
      </button>

      <view class="split-text">或</view>

      <!-- 只保留这一个微信按钮 -->
      <button
        class="wechat-btn"
        loading="{{wxLoading}}"
        disabled="{{loading || wxLoading}}"
        open-type="getPhoneNumber"
        bindgetphonenumber="onGetPhoneNumber"
      >
        {{wxLoading ? '登录中...' : '微信快捷登录'}}
      </button>

      <view class="wx-tip">
        默认优先使用微信手机号快捷登录，未授权手机号时会自动切换为微信快捷登录
      </view>

      <view class="bottom-row">
        <text class="bottom-text">还没有账号？</text>
        <text class="register-link" bindtap="goRegister">手机号注册</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>